Remove the first line of initialization.sql. It may cause your thing to crash if the user is not called postgres.

Create trigger that inserts anyone inserted into faculty or student into the user details with a default password.

Create a new role as soon as a new user is created and allow the user to inherit the roles that were set up for admin, faculty and student.

If the credit limit is less than 18, set the credit limit to 18 and if the credit limit is greater than 24, set the credit limit to 24

The same course code cannot be offered by different departments